{
  "stem": "4670.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it wasn't much after that, I think it was two weeks after I got my winter coat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was very cold already in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The wind was blowing, and my mother and I were downtown.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We had been shopping in a department store.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And when we come rounding a corner, we ran smack into the immigration officer that had actually deported us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He pointed his finger and my mother and I, we began to ran-- to run.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But we knew we'd be found.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There's no question about that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had no choice but to go back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that point, it was in 19-- let's see, that was the end of 19-- it was October 1934.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think was the end of 1934.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We then began to send telegrams and letters to the USA, and we really didn't get response.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I don't think I'll ever forget the day that we went across that border.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we were on the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was like-- it's almost like if you-- I visualize a person who might be-- have been in a burning house, they will always have the smell of that something that's been singed.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's how I felt when we got on that train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had not looked at any brown shirt stormtroopers all those-- this whole time, and I had sort of taken it out of my memory.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there they were.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we got across the border, the SS-- not the SS, not the black-shirted, the SR, the brown ones, got on the train.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to show your papers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they asked us where are you going?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we said we're going to Frankfurt.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
